    "description": "The IPBAR1420 PRO is the professional led bar with lots of options.\n\nIPBAR1420 PRO is a Led bar with 14 times 20w RGBWA led and with an IP65 makes it one of the safest choices on the market.\nBecause it is not enough that it has extremely beautiful colors, there is also the possibility of building several units together into one and mounting brackets are in several places.\nAt the same time, all LEDs can also be controlled individually so that running effects and pixel maps can be created.",
